```python
def insert_after_character(string):
    return string.replace('c', 'cG')

print(insert_after_character('abcde'))  # abGcde
print(insert_after_character('ccc'))  # cGcGcG
print(insert_after_character(''))  # ''
print(insert_after_character('G'))  # G
print(insert_after_character('c'))  # cG
```
